flowchart LR
    Internet[互联网/不受信任网络]
    Corp[办公网/VPN]
    App[应用运行区]
    Bastion[运维堡垒机]
    Gateway[认证网关/反向代理]

    subgraph MQVPC[RocketMQ 专用 VPC]
        Proxy[Proxy]
        NS[NameServer]
        Broker[Broker 集群]
        Controller[Controller 集群]
        Dashboard[Dashboard]
        Metrics[监控与日志组件]
    end

    Internet -- 默认拒绝 --> MQVPC
    Corp --> Bastion
    Bastion --> Gateway
    Gateway --> Dashboard
    Gateway --> Metrics

    App -- TLS + ACL --> Proxy
    App -- 经典客户端: TLS + ACL --> NS
    App -- 经典客户端: TLS + ACL --> Broker

    Proxy --> NS
    Proxy --> Broker
    Broker --> Controller
    NS --> Broker
